[thinking] **Evaluating test coverage**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering the action related to the native-image run failing for existing tests. It seems those tests don’t actually cover the OAuth2WebClient. However, it’s interesting to note that "meaningful coverage" is still reachable without involving OAuth2. I think this means we might not need to include OAuth2 in the test coverage at this point. I'm curious about how to approach this problem effectively to ensure we have sufficient testing in place!
